D: "Example 1: String Length & Case Conversion"
D: "js\nlet message = \"JavaScript is fun!\";\nconsole.log(message.length); // 18\nconsole.log(message.toUpperCase()); // JAVASCRIPT IS FUN!\n"
D: "We found the length of the string and changed it to uppercase!"

