D: "Example 2: Extracting & Replacing Text"
D: "js\nlet text = \"I love coding!\";\nconsole.log(text.slice(2, 6)); // \"love\"\nconsole.log(text.replace(\"coding\", \"JavaScript\")); // \"I love JavaScript!\"\n"
D: "With .slice(), we extract part of the text, and with .replace(), we change a word!"

